{"tid":1383631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[救火小隊] 有冇可能可以用CBRN頂級防毒面罩再加hazmat suit","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T18:28:33.000Z","uid":293770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7733e461656d27b04a3a0c5ea0d7302160af5a06","tid":1383631,"uid":293770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:32:07.000Z","msg":"CBRN=Chemical, Biological, Radiological, Nuclear<br />\n<br />\n因為市面上大多數嘅防毒面罩都唔係為防 tear gas 而設；同埋救火小隊佢哋要面對高濃度嘅催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大多數裝備只有短袖衫又或者好薄嘅衣物；令到被灼傷嘅風險非常高<br />\n<br />\n咁樣用一個好似打生化戰爭嘅裝備就令前線要經常接觸催淚彈嘅人安全性提高<br />\n<br />\n缺點就係放毒面罩一個要成幾千銀可能要眾籌；不過考慮到救火人士可能只係得100人以內其實係可行<br />\n<br />\n同埋有巴打證明到海關係可以比呢啲物品過關<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhjPrJt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhjPrJt.png&h=9177a0de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f460850a212b35c8ba585d741b72bd2526ad7db7","tid":1383631,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"Hazmat suit嘅機動性低<br />\n同埋好多動作都未必做到 驚整穿<br />\n<br />\n反而CBRN Mask有得諗"},{"pid":"5053a05fc8c8f0d0a35cb50d4025d6c65f1ca622","tid":1383631,"uid":293770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f460850a212b35c8ba585d741b72bd2526ad7db7","tid":1383631,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"Hazmat suit嘅機動性低<br />\n同埋好多動作都未必做到 驚整穿<br />\n<br />\n反而CBRN Mask有得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"中唯一方法係咪用雨褸。了？"},{"pid":"b17c229b4dccdcc6b78608e34109cacf3f4023ad","tid":1383631,"uid":17973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f460850a212b35c8ba585d741b72bd2526ad7db7","tid":1383631,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"Hazmat suit嘅機動性低<br />\n同埋好多動作都未必做到 驚整穿<br />\n<br />\n反而CBRN Mask有得諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:37:54.000Z","msg":"CBRN Mask，已經講緊係自帶氧氣樽個種。<br />\n<br />\n要買都係Mil-Spec的Gas Mask。"},{"pid":"146619d7c6f8ace13fad863acff2a54a1d0bc564","tid":1383631,"uid":254581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b17c229b4dccdcc6b78608e34109cacf3f4023ad","tid":1383631,"uid":17973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f460850a212b35c8ba585d741b72bd2526ad7db7","tid":1383631,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"Hazmat suit嘅機動性低<br />\n同埋好多動作都未必做到 驚整穿<br />\n<br />\n反而CBRN Mask有得諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:37:54.000Z","msg":"CBRN Mask，已經講緊係自帶氧氣樽個種。<br />\n<br />\n要買都係Mil-Spec的Gas Mask。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:42:02.000Z","msg":"s10?"},{"pid":"d704fe155c412a8261b98be5bf9736faf0c1d40e","tid":1383631,"uid":17973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"146619d7c6f8ace13fad863acff2a54a1d0bc564","tid":1383631,"uid":254581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b17c229b4dccdcc6b78608e34109cacf3f4023ad","tid":1383631,"uid":17973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f460850a212b35c8ba585d741b72bd2526ad7db7","tid":1383631,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"Hazmat suit嘅機動性低<br />\n同埋好多動作都未必做到 驚整穿<br />\n<br />\n反而CBRN Mask有得諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:37:54.000Z","msg":"CBRN Mask，已經講緊係自帶氧氣樽個種。<br />\n<br />\n要買都係Mil-Spec的Gas Mask。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:42:02.000Z","msg":"s10?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:50:15.000Z","msg":"或者Israel 出緊 Mask，最平。淘寶就FMJ 10。"},{"pid":"b80be602e158041e33e756f445662914823b0eee","tid":1383631,"uid":254581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d704fe155c412a8261b98be5bf9736faf0c1d40e","tid":1383631,"uid":17973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"146619d7c6f8ace13fad863acff2a54a1d0bc564","tid":1383631,"uid":254581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b17c229b4dccdcc6b78608e34109cacf3f4023ad","tid":1383631,"uid":17973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim